Before this 'The Witch' was considered Brian's best app. I can now confirm that 'The Witch' is Brian's second best app. This beats the witch hand over fist. The graphics are amazing and the responses are clear. It's easy to use, just turn on and carry out your session. Remember to record your sessions externally as screen recorders will not work with this app. Don't stop with this app though, purchase 'The Witch' as well. You will then have Brian's best two for under ¬£10. Bargain.
